  <summary>Spoilers</summary>
  I like how we got the backstory of the new programmer, Narumi because ever since she joined Eagle Jump, she seemed way too perfect -- being able to program games really quick with no errors or any bugs at all. <br /><br />

  As for the New Game season 2 ending, I love in the grand reveal of their newest game PECO, Ko-chan, or Yagami credited Aoba for her character designer and told Aoba to come up stage, which Aoba didn't expect at all. The final episode was a very emotional episode since the face of Eagle Jump, Yagami, revealed to the whole company, not just Rin, that she is leaving to go to France and work on games. <br /><br />

  I'm almost certain that New Game season 3 will come out, and some hopes for season 3 are: <br /><br />
